cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper proposes an object detector for top-view grid maps. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions range sensor measurements and the proposed method can be applied to robotic systems. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper proposes a joint model that improves generalization through regularization and investigates different model architectures. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a method that generates training data automatically without manual annotations. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper proposes a method that can be applied to control systems with range sensor measurements.
